bove the joists, between the deck boards and the framing. Channels water to gutters and downspouts. Invisible from below you see the bare joists. Best for: homeowners who want dry space below without finishing the ceiling."}],"$L4","$L5"]}],"$L6","$L7","$L8","$L9"]}],"$La","$Lb","$Lc","$Ld","$Le",["$Lf","$L10","$L11"],"$L12","$L13"]}]}],"$L14","$L15"],["$L16"],"$L17"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"Jebrcr4Vyd2YosxlccnHN"}
